General.Name: Divio Technologies AB Series B
General.Description: Divio Technologies AB (publ) engages in the development and sale of software platforms that allows companies to build, operate, and maintain complex websites in a cloud-based infrastructure. The company's platform enables enterprise IT departments to create websites and dynamic web apps by managing cloud infrastructure, as well as offering flexible, secure, and high-performance solutions that easily scale with growing business needs. It also handles migration and management of external and internal web-based applications in the cloud services. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
